{"tid":1157342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"房間內自慰被撞破 保守父母裝CCTV","createTime":"2019-05-16T08:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T08:47:41.000Z","uid":202488,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb58427a648ff30a49194b1208ca940b2a3f2ad","tid":1157342,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打飛機都唔得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做聖人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不少父母都害怕與子女談及性，開放如西方國家也不例外，美國有父母撞破15歲兒子自慰後，竟然要求兒子承諾不會再自慰，並在房間及浴室裝CCTV以防「再犯」，使兒子崩潰向網民求救，甚至揚言要起訴父母侵犯私慰。<br />\n<br />\n來自美國阿拉斯加的15歲少年，日前在網上討論區「Reddit」發文，指本月自己在房間內自慰，卻不幸被父親撞破，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">父親沒有敲門就闖進來，見狀便即尖叫著，然後父母坐下與我傾談，告訴我不能這樣做。」<br />\n禁兒子上性教育課</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於其父母性格非常保守，不但反對婚前性行為，甚至阻止他參加學校舉辦的性教育課程。事發之後，父母即指會在其房內安裝閉路電視，以防他再次自慰。其父母甚至表示會在浴室裝上鏡頭，即使他已強烈反對，但父親表示：<br />\n<br />\n「你答應我不會再自慰，這是為了讓你遵守承諾。」<br />\n事主發現父母果然已網購鏡頭，父親亦強調會每日檢查，以確定他不敢自慰。<br />\n<br />\n少年：我有權觸摸自己的身體<br />\n<br />\n事主對父母的舉動感到憤怒，認為令他非常尷尬，完全侵犯了他的隱私，更揚言要起訴父母，遂向網民尋求法律意見。他直言：<br />\n<br />\n「我已經15歲了，我有權觸摸自己的身體。」<br />\n事件引起網民熱議，有人指出：「無論你有否自慰，你在使用浴室和換衫時都應該要有隱私。」有人則強調自慰實屬正常不過的事，完全不需要羞恥，批評涉事父母行為過份。有人則建議事主向身邊其他成年人求助，透過他們嘗試說服父母和改變他們的想法。"},{"pid":"ff4dc40fe0b706def4f48998a48b1c49cc495102","tid":1157342,"uid":202488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"尖乜撚野叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40c2ea6bb420d4d75603a3bb3a4901d4b0286ee","tid":1157342,"uid":206152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:17:02.000Z","msg":"出街打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ca76d6f7ef95d429d9a94e72104d5ec10e2e52","tid":1157342,"uid":212024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:17:06.000Z","msg":"一早有人出左po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5b808e7d3bb9c5bbad437fbe5dce7787e2ba11","tid":1157342,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"On9老豆後生係打過飛機？"},{"pid":"131315ea812cc21e35f9fb38f16a05b37b62bd6e","tid":1157342,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"耶撚？"},{"pid":"5629a60295dc042f5281060803265ca44ff6d01f","tid":1157342,"uid":205449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04ca76d6f7ef95d429d9a94e72104d5ec10e2e52","tid":1157342,"uid":212024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:17:06.000Z","msg":"一早有人出左po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:29:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬永遠慢三拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479201e4b67ec4b3d653a99aa1a50acd0e3501ca","tid":1157342,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04ca76d6f7ef95d429d9a94e72104d5ec10e2e52","tid":1157342,"uid":212024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:17:06.000Z","msg":"一早有人出左po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:37:25.000Z","msg":"我做野唔洗你教,你唔好再阿芝阿佐"},{"pid":"c13c78165442bbf40e379a061a672b4cc769de46","tid":1157342,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"131315ea812cc21e35f9fb38f16a05b37b62bd6e","tid":1157342,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"耶撚？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img sr